WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.770
We bring them cloud usage, they bring us sales acceleration.

00:00:04.770 --> 00:00:09.540
This is a simple physical exchange. AppsFlyer is a major

00:00:09.540 --> 00:00:14.310
customer of their infrastructure. When our platform scales, our cloud

00:00:14.310 --> 00:00:19.080
utilization increases, which directly expands Amazon's bottom line.
